manifest_analysis.title:
Broadcast Receiver (com.google.firebase.iid.FirebaseInstanceIdReceiver) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: com.google.android.c2dm.permission.SEND
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.
manifest_analysis.name: is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.[android:exported=true]

stack_canary.description: This shared object has a stack canary value added to the stack so that it will be overwritten by a stack buffer that overflows the return address. This allows detection of overflows by verifying the integrity of the canary before function return.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object has full RELRO enabled. RELRO ensures that the GOT cannot be overwritten in vulnerable ELF binaries. In Full RELRO, the entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) is marked as read-only.

playstore_details.title: HitBTC – Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading BTC App
playstore_details.description:
Meet the best cryptocurrency trading app!
HitBTC exchange founded in 2013 was created by leading technical minds, high-level finance, and experienced bitcoin trading professionals. The HitBTC crypto trading app provides a secure, effective, and fast way to trade bitcoin and cryptocurrencies on your mobile phone. Use your favorite tools and features for versatile bitcoin and crypto trading, just under your fingertips.

Cutting-Edge Matching Engine
Platform’s core engine is among the best technological products in its class for real-time clearing and order matching algorithms.

High Liquidity Exchange
Trading volume exceeds one billion US dollars daily. Moreover, a Rebate system for order makers rewarding each trader, whose monthly trading volume exceeds 100 BTC. The more you trade, the more bitcoins you get!

Supported crypto assets
Trade Bitcoin and over 500 cryptocurrency assets like Ethereum (ETH), Ripple’s XRP, Binance Coin (BNB), Litecoin (LTC), Monero (XMR), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Tether (USDT), and so on! New coins are regularly added to exchange after the strict compliance check.

High-Level Security
Account access is available strictly through API keys and PIN-code. Plus, the advanced data encryption technology and highly protected cold storage to keep your bitcoins SAFU.

Trading Tools & Indicators
Different trading types including Market, Good-Till-Cancelled, Immediate-Or-Cancel, Fill-or-Kill, Day, Good-Till-Date/Time. Advanced trading indicators for a smooth bitcoin trading strategy: Moving Average, Bollinger Bands, MACD, Relative Strength Index, etc.

Convenient Asset Management
Deposit, transfer, and withdraw your bitcoins and cryptocurrency assets anytime and anywhere.

Multilingual Support
Trade Bitcoin in English, Spanish, Portuguese, and Indonesian (Bahasa) languages. Multilingual customer support works round-the-clock.
